{
  "stem": "1338.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he lived in that area.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He wasn't that rich, obviously.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And of course, he made some deal with Jews who wanted to go there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he moved to their apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He didn't do it necessarily because he wanted to throw them out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Actually, he used to bring food to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the interesting thing was, this father, his life was Polish, and his son was raised as a Pole.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But as soon as the Germans came in, they all became the so-called, Volksdeutsche, which is the Germans of the occupied territories.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And strangely enough, he was warning us always about his son, because he's going to join Hitler, he's going to be, you know, a German.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And of course, the father couldn't stand that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so he bring us food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he arranged for us to move into one of his-- he had a building there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "A building-- it was four rooms, and an outhouse, and a little closet in front of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so we moved there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he would come and see us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he helped us to move there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we did not suffer from the terrible situation of moving to a ghetto, not knowing where to go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would herd three, four families in one room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, people would just go in and try to occupy places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a mess.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So at least we had a very orderly transfer, because Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], which was his name, and was a very fine man-- helped us to move there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at least, even though we got in the room, which was probably smaller-- just about my office size-- it was a little stove with the chimney is going up.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Actually, I cut myself on the chimney once.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And here it is.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
